{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"978119e3b4","title":"中央首长第二次接见青海代表会议记录","origin":"刊载于《中央首长讲话》（3），北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编，1967年4月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"afad18f353","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":21,"articleId":"978119e3b4"}],"tags":[{"id":"00506c3c84","name":"关锋","type":"人物"},{"id":"06af9ed14a","name":"肖华","type":"人物"},{"id":"20ebde32a6","name":"王力","type":"人物"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"},{"id":"5f4cf2fdf4","name":"青海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"6767f054ce","name":"穆欣","type":"人物"},{"id":"6d76320c28","name":"刘贤权","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"},{"id":"ef71f03227","name":"中央文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"8bb7755376","name":"康生"},{"id":"fa147b61e7","name":"王力"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"175cdc2c17","type":"title","text":"中央首长第二次接见青海代表会议记录","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"01ade2a2ac","type":"authors","text":"陈伯达康生王力","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"d1357b28a0","type":"appellation","text":"〖时间：夜至22日凌晨，地点：政协礼堂。出席：陈伯达、康生、王力、关锋、戚本禹、穆欣、肖华。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"17f7b8aeb4","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：宣布一条，这里什么话都可以讲。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"539c8172fc","type":"paragraph","text":"陈代海：二十三日早上六点多钟戒严了，11点左右……","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"89696474de","type":"paragraph","text":"肖：两点左右，楼有多高？","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"52b9207dca","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：有五层多高……有爆炸声不是手榴弹就是……我们也不敢看了，过了一会儿，×××就都进来了。……我亲眼看见一个解放军讲：昨天你还和我辩论，捍卫队就打你。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"54090cf792","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：捍卫队打人？","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"f9407f5125","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：打，×××也有人打人……","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"0a681c877b","type":"paragraph","text":"张惠英：我在报社，哪 里都可以去。事后他们对我讲，这些死人都是从帐蓬里拉出来的。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"d54bb046e9","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你多大？爸爸干什么？（答……）报社有没有枪？","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"d6427daa6c","type":"paragraph","text":"张：没有。我有证件哪儿都可以去。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"e568c05868","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：报社楼上有没有枪？","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"8c09bde49f","type":"paragraph","text":"金莱：我在报社，楼上我都去过，没看见枪。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"a03f265533","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：二十三日你们谁在楼上？","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"5515e2f899","type":"paragraph","text":"王建义：我在。……没看见有枪。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"b39e60aba2","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：小桥死人最多？","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"da4cba9ed5","type":"paragraph","text":"陈存秀：我在小桥。……军区的嗽叭先宣布八·一八是“反革命”。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"1af36d0559","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：军队的车宣布的？","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"ad9c4d1244","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：……有人叫我把头低下，我就听到前面有枪从北向南打。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"b7445927e7","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：谁先开的枪？","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"6dfda30830","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：军队从北向南打。","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"c7b641d297","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：步枪？机关枪？","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"a166cd3e93","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：步枪。","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"b394a8627c","type":"paragraph","text":"（肖、王、关看图）","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"2925816cf4","type":"paragraph","text":"关：第一枪喇叭没打坏？","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"b63f8899c0","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：11点停止广播。他们叫我们11点停止广播，否则一切后果由八·一八负责。","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"2e15761118","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：他们11点10分开枪。","index":27,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"7214a03053","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：……有四五排手挽手……（肖分外注意、戚微笑、关吸烟安祥视肖）","index":28,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"7eada709e1","type":"paragraph","text":"关：四五排？工人、学生？","index":29,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"a89faf9766","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：工人们都手挽手站着。……（突然咽住不讲）","index":30,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"2a0327548d","type":"paragraph","text":"关：讲吧。（无声）那些人怎么死的？","index":31,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"487174ea0a","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：……两点左右从宾馆打来两颗信号弹，两个教练弹，天空有炸开飞的纸机，听到的全是机枪声。","index":32,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"ddd89e5755","type":"paragraph","text":"关：不是报社里先开的枪？","index":33,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"eed8defde4","type":"paragraph","text":"相喜：我们的同志在里面。","index":34,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"9af6a7f3ab","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：工人们一排排的倒下，为避免不必要的牺牲，我们撤……我们被抓，下午四点捍卫队来抓人，抓出的人都被打的鼻青脸肿，剩下的人，我们学“语录“，唱想念毛主席……后把我们红卫兵放了……","index":35,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"f405979151","type":"paragraph","text":"于桂梅：……那天形势紧张，我们有精神准备，因为知道11点要采取行动。","index":36,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"1910d528e4","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：哪个宾馆住了队伍？","index":37,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"43c5617b76","type":"paragraph","text":"滨友：里面有机枪、探照灯，可以打到小桥。","index":38,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"365a53e6c8","type":"paragraph","text":"关：为什么能打到？","index":39,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"2938a44da5","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：那个地方高？","index":40,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"7d17302d62","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：几挺机枪？","index":41,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"4efb7d092a","type":"paragraph","text":"滨友：两挺吧，不详。","index":42,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"39be22835b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：有照片。（送上王力、肖同来看）","index":43,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"95adef8dc0","type":"paragraph","text":"于桂梅：……北邮的宣传队出去宣传……下一时，打起了枪，不知打到哪儿，只听枪声，报社里面的师傅指枪膛说：“你朝这儿打。”军队叫：不要慌，我们把枪对准一小撮反革命的。停了一会儿，一点多时，形势紧张，一会儿外面枪声紧，大家都去了，正看到一卡车×××在打枪，朝前面一堆人扫射。当时我想不会打死人，没关系，有假枪。后来倒了一排又一排，有人跑，跑到那边也倒。后来在倒下的一堆人上有一人起来了，脸上全是血，我们才知道人打死了。后来车上的人都下来冲进报社了，……叫报社里的人交证件、主席纪念章。……后来了人，照名单宣布反革命，（主要是坚守报社的八·一八和红宣兵）当时抓起一些人捆起来打一顿。一直没见的捍卫队这时全出来了，（关、戚冷笑）来一批老捍抓人，打人，一直到七点，押我们，勒令举手，我们不举，就×× ×××，半路叫我跪下报名……到了省委，他们叫我们按单位分开……后放了，路上见全城戒严。","index":44,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"9a8f7a99f9","type":"paragraph","text":"关：这是二十四日了！","index":45,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"5c80ef8de5","type":"paragraph","text":"于：我们刚一进厂，捍卫队就喊“站住：”，我们没进，到兰州，想汇报中央。","index":46,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"97cee86e50","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：（向小陈）你们那天广播了什么？","index":47,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"3873ba9ff3","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：“首都红卫兵报”“通令”","index":48,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"8f6cd64c0a","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：没别的？","index":49,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"3ee5469341","type":"paragraph","text":"陈：没有。（上交肖一份通令，肖看）","index":50,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"8d6d42e3ff","type":"paragraph","text":"关：（问帐蓬里的情况）（康老、伯达进厅，热烈鼓掌）（戚将麦克风头转向伯达，伯达又风趣地把麦克风头转向戚）","index":51,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"410318e8ce","type":"paragraph","text":"相喜：（重复13日汇报……康十分注意听）","index":52,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"799619e8b8","type":"paragraph","text":"（伯达翻阅青海日报）","index":53,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"d4fe781b1b","type":"paragraph","text":"王：……我挨了一拳。","index":54,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"570aa4be22","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：谁打的？","index":55,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"3ef28ee530","type":"paragraph","text":"王：不知道……我清醒过来以后，有四个背枪的×××……他们打我，给我一张纸，我写了个强烈抗议，他们上来个人打了我个耳光，打完了以后提出了我这是19日。23日就发生了事（重复十四日事）（李平安，孙祥梅入场）。在我们牢一个人受了伤，脸上挨了枪子儿，头被砸烂。我们的男、女同学都被绑起来。有的同学被打的厉害。我们听了第四期社论之后非常难过……给我们同学带上镣拷。每天给两张纸，一张写交代，一张写揭发……。放风的时间一天就五分钟，阴森森的。我们的一个同志在现场也没回来。击倒了一个邮电管理局的同志，从腹部穿过。（康生、伯达一直注意听着）又击中刘凤池……有七十多个人被打得满脸是血，刺刀刺了眼睛……那天大约有八千六百人被捕……我们没有看到“八·一八”有枪。他们讲“八·一八”有枪，又拿不出来。一个×××又讲没枪。三月一日下午五点钟，他们把我们从监狱里押了出来，送到了党校，进行“整训学习”。（实际上，当时党校是一个监狱外的监狱，首都三司和外地红卫兵并没有获得解放）当我们四十四个刚从南滩监狱里出来的同学，被押到党校，强迫我们去礼堂开会，听“卫戍区司令部首长”报告，我们刚进会场，一个“卫戍区司令部首长”问我们是从哪里来的，我们回答说：“南滩监狱里来的”！！当他听我们的口气不对时，他讲：你们不是从南滩监狱里出来的，你们回去后千万不要告诉你们的同学和老师。你们是“集中审查”的，是因为没有地方，借那里（指南滩监狱）的房子用。……（除康老外，众首长皆笑） 我们大的二十二岁、三岁，最小的十五岁。（康老笑问张惠英多大？）","index":56,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"792966b65b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：他（指张）在报社，你谈谈吧？","index":57,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"b41b65e950","type":"paragraph","text":"张：……没想到我们是反革命。（众首长皆笑）我们听到是炮声，同学们讲是枪声。（众首长又笑）","index":58,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"0036b1532b","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：你听过枪声吗？","index":59,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"ab68f3a1a3","type":"paragraph","text":"张：连串的没听过。……三司的宣传车讲我们要坚守岗位。三司的念语录、演节目，许多工人同志都哭了。他们问大家怕不怕，工人答不怕，后唱大海航行靠舵手，……两点左右枪声特别密。我们都吓醒了，……刺刀对准了我们，叫我们举手，我们不举，他们讲你们这样顽固，用枪托打我们……他们念名字许仲仁……这些都是反革命，叫我们互相检举，我们都不说话，他们就让进来的捍卫队、“火车头”认本单位的人，认出去打耳光、大皮鞋猛踢，抓完大头目，抓小头目，再抓广播员打……一个工人受了重伤，医院不给包，这个工人活活地打死了……跪不住就打，有的人就活活打死了，我们的同学有的都哭了，我要上厕所他们不叫，我就跑，骂我小顽固，（康老冷笑）我出来以后，他们就打。……我带你院里参观，朝里院说：“好，你们八·一八自己打死自己人，烧死，脑袋都打掉。”这时已经过了三、四个小时了，不叫别人看，只叫捍卫队看，对我讲：“你看这个小女孩，脑袋都被砸烂了……”他们说：“你们打死自己想投降的人，看你们八·一八”！以后他说：“这些人都是我们从帐蓬里搜出来的，已经烧死好多天了。”……有些帐蓬我经常去，根本就没有见过死人，他后来就叫我回去。我和同学讲了，同学们都不相信。一个×人上来就打，揪掉了我的头发，边打边骂，还抢我的纪念章，我装在口袋里不给，旁边一个人讲：“纪念章不要也可以。”（康老写条传与伯达，伯达传与戚、关……关唤人，关、戚交换意见，伯达过去了。）……他们不光有枪，还有圆盘的枪，（康老点头）……我们上了车……，","index":60,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"34ce54d665","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：（向张）与你讲话的人（说八·一八打死解放军的人）从哪儿进来的。","index":61,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"02ec335602","type":"paragraph","text":"王相喜：（答肖）……在火车上抓我们在车上的同志……他们讲打死了战士，用棺材游行，上面写着“×××烈士”，士兵们的脚趾头都受了伤，“火车头”真“勇敢”（重复14日情况）……一个子弹打伤了脖子的同志，本没死，被剪刀绞断了咽喉死了。","index":62,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"064029d0eb","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：没开枪解放军怎么伤呢？","index":63,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"5e506c5c21","type":"paragraph","text":"王相喜：（解释）","index":64,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"96d79a9011","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：你们的同学回来没有？（答：没有。）应回来反映情况。","index":65,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"ead6428c5e","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：打了电话，昨天……。","index":66,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"a50492c520","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们有数没有？","index":67,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"bfce57a864","type":"paragraph","text":"众：交了。（指同学名单）","index":68,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"57a2dea715","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（对康）给他（指肖）了。","index":69,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"b976e46f79","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：（对金莱）我打了电话了。","index":70,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"7120a11d57","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们在场的人在报社看到枪了没有？","index":71,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"c16fe80f6c","type":"paragraph","text":"众：没有。……我们里面挤着睡。","index":72,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"089c546df4","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：里面睡了两千多人。","index":73,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"f747a7dc84","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：里面是哪个工厂的工人？","index":74,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"ab215fd7d9","type":"paragraph","text":"众：（对小张）你去帐蓬里去看烧死的人有几个？","index":75,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"7ae3ac193f","type":"paragraph","text":"张：四个。","index":76,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"201353bf03","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：死人像几天了？什么样子？比如脸……","index":77,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"193fe52914","type":"paragraph","text":"张：和别的死人的样子一样。","index":78,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"015ce98bb2","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：是烧死的吗？","index":79,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"c11dc365e3","type":"paragraph","text":"张：×人讲是烧的。","index":80,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"757772bde9","type":"paragraph","text":"贾：我们参观时，他们讲是硫酸烧死的……","index":81,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"58aadcac60","type":"paragraph","text":"（戚对肖笑）一个××讲抄去四挺机枪、子弹是在地道里，我们要看，他讲地道口还没找到呢？……血还是鲜红的。","index":82,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"e7eea04c21","type":"paragraph","text":"肖华：有枪眼没有？","index":83,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"264da3d18b","type":"paragraph","text":"贾：他们不叫去，划了一道白线，说是现场。","index":84,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"3be5264c8b","type":"paragraph","text":"肖：是现场？","index":85,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"9a3d8960f1","type":"paragraph","text":"小张：我看时，他们从帐蓬里找出来的，不是现场。","index":86,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"6c6592083c","type":"paragraph","text":"肖：你们参观尸体有多远？","index":87,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"4d43f1a66e","type":"paragraph","text":"小张：……","index":88,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"1e51a7a974","type":"paragraph","text":"肖：几个烧死的？","index":89,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"f48495ebc1","type":"paragraph","text":"小张：四个。","index":90,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"6150dde7e8","type":"paragraph","text":"肖：（对贾）烧死几个？","index":91,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"43ced5139f","type":"paragraph","text":"贾：我见烧死的有一个，胸口有一滩血，其它都是打死的。","index":92,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"363ba55acd","type":"paragraph","text":"（戚拿出一迭照片给参观过的人看）","index":93,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"89fc028258","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：是不是你们参观过的？","index":94,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"5c9b3b9772","type":"paragraph","text":"小张：我看不出来。","index":95,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"876f5e8599","type":"paragraph","text":"（康老点几个有关的学院）","index":96,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"ed26ec5d4e","type":"paragraph","text":"众：……","index":97,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"96e951826d","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（指了一下王相喜，问各学校的同学）（对农机三人）你们二十三日在现场，你们看到有枪没有？","index":98,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"de9afef5c7","type":"paragraph","text":"三人：我们14日进去没看到。","index":99,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"8084c511f1","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：工人换班，有没有可能带进枪去？","index":100,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"6fce63f4c9","type":"paragraph","text":"众：没有。","index":101,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"83e4808d29","type":"paragraph","text":"王相喜：……（伯达出去坐在旁边的椅子上）……有几个××××同意开枪动武。","index":102,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"620a32a258","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：是那个×××师。","index":103,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"e3d6d2d0af","type":"paragraph","text":"众：×××部队。（肖对康耳语）","index":104,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"1f71aaee4f","type":"paragraph","text":"吕：我们怕××栽赃，我们进去时连小刀全不让带。……","index":105,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"408fd05db8","type":"paragraph","text":"相喜：根本没逮捕证，只要是同意“八·一八”全抓。","index":106,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"6fc126d277","type":"paragraph","text":"（金莱交穆欣一份“特大喜讯“，问：真的假的？穆：我不知道，我问肖主任。给肖华）","index":107,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"c59abd1729","type":"paragraph","text":"（金莱向穆欣答：林总那个是假的，兰州那个查一查，看是否青军欺骗兰军）","index":108,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"a4ac4d5ae6","type":"paragraph","text":"王建义：……","index":109,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"6323669378","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：……","index":110,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"1ac1fe789e","type":"paragraph","text":"王建义：我们厂的“老捍“，有人穿着军衣，领章一样不差，有四个人我们认识他，其它厂也可能有，我们厂的四个人我认的准。报社中的帐蓬，我负责搭了一部分，每天我们都去帐蓬里看一看，有没有烤火，烧坏了的，所以我保证里面没烧死人，联络点我也去，保证没有枪。","index":111,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"25fe1d0c52","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：他们有一种说法：……报社里有许多人原是八·一八，后不赞成八·一八，报社中的人就把他打死，是否在这13个人中有没有要出而被打死的？","index":112,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"c5aefad6f6","type":"appellation","text":"众：没有，造谣。","index":113,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"1d3cfbb36a","type":"paragraph","text":"王相义：……","index":114,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"0e62fd7ab9","type":"paragraph","text":"（金莱向穆欣，难道烧死的还有血迹吗？穆对金莱耳语：他们军区做了许多假象，核对一下，可以驳倒他们）","index":115,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"ac7f3725dd","type":"paragraph","text":"相喜：……八·一八在坚持文斗，不用武斗上非常好，当我们拖住报社里“执行任务”的解放军时，他们全有意见。（康频频点头）","index":116,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"54fb283661","type":"paragraph","text":"王建议：解放军吃饼干时我们送水，他们问，你们那么多人怎么烧水？我讲就是我们不喝水，也要让解放军喝水。（当时他们的连长不在）他们讲你们好，不过我们是执行命令。","index":117,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"66703dac9f","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们怎么辩论“六·三”社论？这与我有关。","index":118,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"eef6290e0d","type":"paragraph","text":"众：我们认为好，现在他们要翻案。","index":119,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"cbe900df22","type":"paragraph","text":"金莱：青海日报有个人要找您辩论。","index":120,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"1b0d7a52ce","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：要把我抓走。（笑）陈逸怎样？在北京？","index":121,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"47dc9a523f","type":"paragraph","text":"金莱：他在青海没有生命安全，现在要抓他。","index":122,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"c1bda3e2bf","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：他现在在哪儿？","index":123,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"2f26d2fe5b","type":"paragraph","text":"答：在地院。","index":124,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"8093a7194e","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：怎么在地院？","index":125,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"09670ae9d2","type":"paragraph","text":"金莱：“民和”事件整理材料，老冯是地院东方红的，他谈一谈。","index":126,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"441a486bca","type":"paragraph","text":"冯：（谈黑材料）","index":127,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"c03db558db","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：是不是要烧？","index":128,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"b79d795d8f","type":"paragraph","text":"冯：都要烧，据说已经烧掉了两车。","index":129,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"e8e31c6b19","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：陈逸那时就来了？","index":130,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"9b006b371d","type":"paragraph","text":"冯：……","index":131,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"8702ec3233","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：程光远怎样？","index":132,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"1587d6f334","type":"paragraph","text":"冯：……","index":133,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"a4d4ed93d9","type":"paragraph","text":"金莱：赵永夫态度恶劣。（述谈判情况，去兰州情况）","index":134,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"6118c1803f","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（问一些现象）轧死一个女工怎么回事？","index":135,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"3f4db977d0","type":"paragraph","text":"（关、戚在一边谈笑自若，肖聚精会神）","index":136,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"e37e38346c","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：不是硬冲的！噢，噢……（康老关心二·三事件。谈得有些乱）","index":137,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"6d2989a05f","type":"paragraph","text":"胡长生：（述二·三事件）","index":138,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"19e62ae311","type":"paragraph","text":"滨友：（介绍刘贤权，送上“简报”，关锋同志交给康老）","index":139,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"8f23aa6faa","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：杨植霖怎么样？","index":140,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"28493d3457","type":"paragraph","text":"胡长生：（介绍杨）杨后来支持八·一八。（康点头）","index":141,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"3a64305db1","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：高克亭怎么样？","index":142,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"80b7ef2c3c","type":"paragraph","text":"滨友：八·一八叫他写材料写了不少、……","index":143,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"f11e4ba495","type":"paragraph","text":"胡：他被八·一八游过街，也被捍卫队游过街，他支持八·一八。","index":144,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"70eefd8ba9","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：为什么对高克亭游街？","index":145,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"0ad8279dce","type":"paragraph","text":"胡：他搞经济主义，八·一八游了他一回。","index":146,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"c2ddf8eab2","type":"paragraph","text":"滨友：李芳远也支持八·一八，原来他轰王昭，最近听说和军区发生冲突有点问题。","index":147,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"c4040b4593","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：韩明呢？","index":148,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"bef9330b79","type":"paragraph","text":"陈武军：……","index":149,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"d04c099304","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：军队除了赵永夫以外，你们认为谁还不好？","index":150,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"310070d60b","type":"paragraph","text":"滨友：××……","index":151,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"a1d0c671a1","type":"paragraph","text":"胡长生：一月三十日晚，××和刘贤权接见外地红卫兵时讲：我支持八·一八，我完全同意刘司令员，时隔不久，完全颠倒过来，大骂刘。","index":152,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"f79bd8ac30","type":"paragraph","text":"滨友：冯国良、相喜：电讯从二月二十三日断绝。","index":153,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"b7de0d52a3","type":"paragraph","text":"冯：2月23日我感觉……因为没电话了。","index":154,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"0a3b32faee","type":"paragraph","text":"金莱：（递给肖主任一份要求，即被没收的红卫兵财物，请求肖指示青海军区归还，肖阅后向金莱点头）","index":155,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"1a1625f5f6","type":"paragraph","text":"滨友：军区内支持八·一八的同志被打成反革命的，都百般折磨（戚：你对肖主任讲）","index":156,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"64ffa21c03","type":"paragraph","text":"肖：多少人？","index":157,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"95e3bd9d5e","type":"paragraph","text":"（答：十一人）。","index":158,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"63c5a907a7","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：你们有几个中学生？（举手）这么多，都成了反革命了？（笑声）你是广东的。","index":159,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"5fae5b0b1f","type":"paragraph","text":"吴：对。","index":160,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"ecbc9be555","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：怎么串连串青海去的？","index":161,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"c0b58c7430","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：青海好玩？……（场内十分活跃，……）","index":162,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"570397b76c","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：八·一八发展组织街道上不纯？","index":163,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"e783432ec9","type":"paragraph","text":"胡长生：……八·一八组织大部分是纯的。","index":164,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"4825b750f1","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：有个王仲山搞有许多女人吗？","index":165,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"d1420f6c16","type":"paragraph","text":"胡：有个人经常跟着他，但决没有这样的事。","index":166,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"dd276437d3","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：不是一个人！","index":167,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"3e39eb6120","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：你们有人伪装解放军把枪运走了？","index":168,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"519d9e32ff","type":"paragraph","text":"众：（十分气愤）根本没有！（金莱对穆欣：造谣造到这种程度了！穆欣笑）（康把麦克风转向肖）","index":169,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"c8dcc87700","type":"paragraph","text":"金莱：“人民日报”三月十二日二版头条最后一段怎么办？","index":170,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"2ff62d9a8a","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：恐怕要更正。","index":171,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"e0bea6d1fd","type":"paragraph","text":"关：今天讲的大家出去不要说，什么那个同志参加了，……","index":172,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"da242dca27","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：我们正在调查，你们不要给我们制造困难，你们一说中央文革支持你们，结果你们倒霉。你们造反有理，有理何必急呢？无理才急。在调查时间不要乱说，不要打电话，发信。","index":173,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"ff0f24f08f","type":"paragraph","text":"众：他们抓人！","index":174,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"d8064442b4","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：在北京不许抓人！要抓必须通过公安部、卫戍司令部，还有中央文革，这一点可以讲。","index":175,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"180935d47b","type":"paragraph","text":"王力：今天就到这儿吧！（鼓掌欢送众首长）","index":176,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"},{"id":"4180759172","type":"paragraph","text":" 刊载于《中央首长讲话》（3），北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编，1967年4月。","index":177,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4"}],"page":{"id":"864e7fe2d6","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"978119e3b4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}